INSERT INTO
            proof_compression_jobs_fri (
                l1_batch_number,
                fri_proof_blob_url,
                status,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                batch_created_at,
                protocol_version,
                protocol_version_patch
            )
            VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, NOW(), NOW(), (
                SELECT batch_created_at
                FROM witness_inputs_fri
                WHERE l1_batch_number = $1
            ), $4, $5)
            ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number) DO NOTHING
